                    <span>This is an excellent "Manual".  Most all the info you need if you want to build a hand scribed round log cabin,but no color pictures.   If your looking for technical building info this is your book.  I bought almost every book available on log homes building and I wouldn't be with out this if you plan to build one yourself.  Not much on house plans or pic's though.</span>
                  
